name: KRPTD
description: A virus is a submicroscopic infectious agent that multiplies inside the living cells of an organism. Viruses infect all life forms, from animals and plants to microorganisms. A computer virus is a type of computer program that, when executed, replicates itself by modifying other computer programs and inserting its own code. If this succeeds, the affected areas are then said to be "infected". In the crypto age, the divisions threaten to unite.
